  "instructions": [
    "Heat the copper pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the olive oil, garlic, and ginger. Cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the turkey mince and cook, breaking it up with a spoon, until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add 100ml water to the pot and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 15 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and crumbled feta cheese (if using).",
    "Continue to cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the dried apricots (if using) and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Sprinkle with additional parsley and feta cheese (if desired) before serving."
